1. *Crkvi* su se okupile svečano da bi proslavile praznik. (The churches gathered solemnly to celebrate the holiday.)

2. On je išao u *crkvu* da se pomoli. (He went to church to pray.)

3. Mladoženja je došao u *crkvu* u svojoj najboljoj odori. (The groom came to the church in his best attire.)

4. Ona je stigla u *crkvu* u trenutku dok su zvonili zvona. (She arrived at the church as the bells were ringing.)

5. *Crkveni* zbor je nastupio da proslavi praznik. (The church choir performed to celebrate the holiday.)